services-cost-money: Unfortunately some services Serble operates cost money to run, this is why we have to impose usage limits on some things. We pride ourselves on being mostly a free service run as a hobby, but we also want to keep the lights on.

I would like to increase the number of projects that are available to the public, so if you have any suggestions for new projects, or any feedback, please contact me through [one of these methods].

swift-description: SWIFT is a user-inclusive browser extension created by 4 entrepreneurs. After weeks of deliberation and creating, SWIFT was developed. A free browser extension that allows user to vote on whether a domain is trustworthy or flag them as suspicious. With both a free and paid model, SWIFT is inclusive to all kinds of users, from those who just want the bare minimum for free, to those who want the full experience at a very fair price.
setup-totp-instructions: On your chosen TOTP app (Some apps you could use include Authy, Microsoft Authenticator, Google Authenticator) scan the QR code below and setup your account. Once you have setup your account, enter the code it provides you into the box to the right and click submit.
totp-warning: If you proceed to setup up 2FA then you will be required to enter a code from your TOTP app every time you login. If you lose access to your TOTP app then you will lose access to your account.
